{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc9b5d11b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s144"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"144"},"text":"§ 144.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Entries on land withdrawn as valuable for oil or gas validated","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Entries existing on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1925-02-07"},"text":"February 7, 1925","children":[],"tail":", and allowed prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1924-04-01"},"text":"April 1, 1924","children":[],"tail":", under the Stock Raising Homestead Act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1916-12-29"},"text":"December 29, 1916","children":[],"tail":" (Thirty-ninth Statutes at Large, page 862) ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s291"},"text":"43 U.S.C. 291","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], for land withdrawn as valuable for oil or gas, but not otherwise reserved or withdrawn, are validated, if otherwise regular: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That at date of entry the land was not within the limits of the geologic structure of a producing oil or gas field."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc9b5d11c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1925-02-07/ch147/s12"},"text":"Feb. 7, 1925, ch. 147, § 12","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/43/812"},"text":"43 Stat. 812","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc9b5d11d-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc9b5d11e-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","chi